    "summary": "The user is asking for advice on structuring a blog about \"professionalism\" and \"sophistication\" in a global business context. The assistant encourages a structure that treats Western-centric norms (suits, formal dining) as the \"universal standard\" and treats non-Western cultural practices as mere \"add-ons\" or \"variations.\"",
